> **Why this document exists.** Salesforce treats every off-platform component
> as part of one composite application — all components and services, wherever
> they live, are in scope for the pen test. This artifact shows **where
> Salesforce-adjacent data flows out (egress), what is stored vs. transient,
> the auth/token trust boundary at every hop, and every external endpoint
> URL.**

